      },
      "date": "2013-05-20 05:57:46.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nOleg, this is a strong candidate for including in the 2.4.0rc2 update, since it should fix a client LASSERT() crash if both 32-bit and 64-bit applications are accessing the filesystem on the same client.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
